{"tid":122610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吳文遠涉與羅便臣道襲擊案有關將到中區警署協助調查","createTime":"2017-02-16T07:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T08:43:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"993e5b225bf3e97bb9221f864a8d930f256a4eb8","tid":122610,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=923596&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D923596%26csid%3D261_341&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=901400f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=923596&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n吳文遠涉與羅便臣道襲擊案有關將到中區警署協助調查<br />\n16.02.2017 13:48<br />\n<br />\n吳文遠在facebook稱警方要求他協助調查涉羅便臣道襲擊案<br />\n社民連主席吳文遠表示，警方早上上門拘捕不果，其後致電給他，指與中區羅便臣道一宗襲擊案有關。他說，下午三時會到中區警署協助調查。<br />\n<br />\n去年9月4日立法會換屆選舉投票日，行政長官梁振英與太太梁唐清儀早上前往羅便臣道票站投票。期間吳文遠涉嫌向梁振英掟出臭魚三文治，警方將事件列為普通襲擊調查。"},{"pid":"3b72e0c17b9ad255814fbdf1e62ac435d3df45bc","tid":122610,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:11:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20170216_20170216-135722.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20170216_20170216-135722.jpg&h=a425193f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d630458a3dfbc0bd262ca4c2b8187601e16c02c","tid":122610,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:18:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f1bcba0d8ab121bb7ab3b4c00d2e2502e20b18f","tid":122610,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:43:06.000Z","msg":"學毓炆出本新書囉<br />\n炆遠新書 襲擊梁振英～～現已接受預購"}]}